    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>rice vinegar</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>sesame oil</strong> and <strong>red chilli relish </strong>to a bowl</p><p>Add 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span><strong> sugar </strong>and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>sticky chilli sauce</strong></p>",
